      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Harika i\u015F \xE7\u0131kard\u0131n!\r\nBug\xFCn kamp alan\u0131n\u0131
    daha g\xFCvenli hale getirdin.\r\n\r\n- K\xF6zleri s\xF6nd\xFCrd\xFCn ve K\xF6z
    S\xF6nd\xFCr\xFCc\xFCs\xFC Rozeti kazand\u0131n.\r\n\r\n- Riskli nesneleri buldun
    ve Do\u011Fa Dedektifi Rozeti kazand\u0131n.\r\n\r\n- Duman g\xF6rd\xFC\u011F\xFCnde
    112\u2019yi araman gerekti\u011Fini \xF6\u011Frendin ve Acil Yard\u0131mc\u0131
    Rozeti kazand\u0131n.\r\n\r\nArt\u0131k kamp alanlar\u0131nda daha dikkatli ve
    bilin\xE7li davranmay\u0131 biliyorsun.\r\n\r\nK\xF6p\xFCk seninle gurur duyuyor!"
